In The Loop Vol 1!!!! 
Friday, January 27th! Join me in celebrating my birthday and the launch of my label, In The Loop 2.0!
I am thrilled to be relaunching my Original imprint, In The Loop. When I started the label in 2015, I envisioned eventually turning it into a well-rounded brand. We are kicking off our season of pop-up events that will continue throughout the year featuring up-and-coming names from all over the work and industry veterans.
In The Loop has hosted events in cities such as Los Angeles, Miami, and New York and features releases from producers like Todd Terry, Kerri Chandler, Junior Sanchez, and more!
What better way to start the new year?

Sometimes, the ones who seem most confident and independent are the ones suffering the most in silence. Be kind to people around you. You really never know what people are going through behind closed doors.
The reason I decided to post this video is to break the stigma that comes with mental health and to show you that you are not alone. It happens to me, too! 
If you are going through something like this, Therapy has helped me immensely over the years, actively learning to love myself and sticking around those who support you in your journey.
I am sending so much love to all my followers / cyber friends who have supported my journey and transformation since 2006. 
I will get back up, and you can too. You have to make it a habit, to keep going even when it hurts.

To all the people supporting me in my journey: I love you 💓
To all my haters: I am not going anywhere 👹 and I love you too because you are the biggest lessons and I am in constant evolution 
This Friday I am playing in San Diego @spinnightclub @fngrscrssd 
With a handful of talented DJs and producers. 
I will be playing a few of my unreleased tunes and edits I’ve been creating in the studio 😎
Last week was full of growing pains and healing for me #metamorphosis 🦋

In a world of uncertainty, I found my way,
Like a newborn, with no parents to guide my day.
A blank canvas, a fresh start, a chance to grow,
As I embarked on a journey to let my true self show.

The self, a complex realm, often misunderstood,
A puzzle of emotions, both bad and good.
Disorder it may seem, but within lies the key,
To unlock the potential, the essence of me.

For in the chaos, lies the beauty untamed,
A kaleidoscope of colors, unashamed.
The self is a tapestry, woven with care,
Each thread a unique story, beyond compare.

So I embrace the imperfections, the flaws I see,
For they are the marks of a life lived free.
No longer bound by the chains of conformity,
I dance to the rhythm of my own individuality.

It was like I was reborn, a phoenix in flight,
With no parents, no boundaries, no darkness in sight.
I embrace the unknown, with a heart unafraid,
For it is in the journey, that true growth is made.
Music by me

Hey there, music lovers! Get ready for an electrifying Sunday in LA! Mark your calendars for December 3rd because you won't want to miss out on an unforgettable night of music.

I'm thrilled to announce that I'll be sharing the stage with some incredible artists: @diplo , @hugelthug , @cocoandbreezy . It's going to be an epic lineup that'll have you dancing all day/night long!

Calling all the Latino gang out there - this is your chance to come together and celebrate our vibrant culture through the power of music. I will be opening, so get there early; make sure to secure your tickets right away!

To purchase your tickets, just head to the link in my stories. 
Trust me, you won't want to miss it!

Get ready to groove, LA! Let's make this Sunday a day/night to remember. See you there!

Dear fans,

I am incredibly grateful and touched by the number of people who have been streaming my music. It truly warms my heart and humbles me deeply. For years, I have faced challenges when it comes to sharing my art with the world, but your support and connection to my music has made it all worthwhile.

To all those who feel a deep connection to my music, please know that I love you all. Your support means the world to me. And I am thrilled to announce that I have more music coming soon, so stay tuned!

As a token of my appreciation, I have a little gift for you: a FREE DOWNLOAD.

Thank you once again for your incredible support.

With love and gratitude, Lupe

🌟 Reflecting on 2023, it was a year filled with growth and transformation in various aspects of my life. I have embraced the valuable lesson of letting go of things that no longer serve a purpose, allowing myself to be more authentic and true to my inner self. This journey of self-discovery extends beyond my identity as an artist; it encompasses my identity as a woman.

🐍 One of the greatest blessings I have received is learning to trust my intuition and listen to the whispers of my soul. This newfound connection with my inner self has been instrumental in my artistic endeavors, allowing me to achieve significant milestones in my creative process.

🙏🏽 I want to express my heartfelt gratitude to all my friends who have accompanied me on this beautiful journey of life, music, and art. Your support and presence have meant the world to me.

⚡️Los amo mucho. As we enter 2024, I am thrilled to share that I have been quietly working on a multitude of musical surprises that stem from the depths of my soul. Stay tuned, as I will be revealing more in the near future. ⚡️
